{"id":3284,"date":"2020-08-13T10:28:08","date_gmt":"2020-08-13T03:28:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/chiprfid.vn\/?p=3284"},"modified":"2020-08-13T10:28:08","modified_gmt":"2020-08-13T03:28:08","slug":"the-rfid-cho-dong-vat-trong-nganh-cong-nghiep-chan-nuoi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/the-rfid-cho-dong-vat-trong-nganh-cong-nghiep-chan-nuoi\/","title":{"rendered":"Th\u1ebb RFID Cho \u0110\u1ed9ng V\u1eadt Trong Ng\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Nghi\u1ec7p Ch\u0103n Nu\u00f4i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i gia s\u00fac kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u1edd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gia t\u0103ng n\u0103ng su\u1ea5t, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i \u01b0u, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cung c\u1ea5p ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ecbt \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 v\u1ec7 sinh an to\u00e0n th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi trong ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i gia s\u00fac l\u00e0 theo d\u00f5i t\u1eebng c\u00e1 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u1eeb l\u00fac m\u1edbi sinh \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00f2 m\u1ed5 b\u1eb1ng th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang &#8211; s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ng\u00e0y sinh, ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng, v.v. &#8211; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u tr\u1eef tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t con chip th\u00f4ng qua c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 RFID &#8211; Radio-Frequency IDentification (nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 tuy\u1ebfn)<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/www.themeatsite.com\/uploads\/files\/articles\/rfid1.jpg\" alt=\"pig rfid research\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Con chip \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00fang v\u00e0o c\u00e1c th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecdc l\u00e0 2-3 m\u00e9t khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ebb t\u1eeb 25 \u0111\u1ebfn 27mm g\u1eafn \u1edf tai \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ecdc 2W<\/p>\n<p>Th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt RFID UHF l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 trong \u0111\u00f3 l\u1edbp UHF th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng (passive UHF Inlay) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n (kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y), \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u1edf nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 220 \u00b0 C v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 vi m\u1ea1ch m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty Impinj &#8211; Chip Monza4D.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/chiprfid.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41H5K4vjV1L._AC_.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3285\" src=\"https:\/\/chiprfid.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41H5K4vjV1L._AC_-411x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"411\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41H5K4vjV1L._AC_-411x400.jpg 411w, https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41H5K4vjV1L._AC_.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 411px) 100vw, 411px\" \/><\/a><br \/>\nGi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p RFID bao g\u1ed3m \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ecdc UHF t\u0129nh (ph\u00e2n c\u1ef1c tr\u00f2n) v\u00e0 di \u0111\u1ed9ng, th\u1ebb UHF g\u1eafn tr\u00ean tai \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ec3 thu th\u1eadp d\u1eef li\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t th\u1ebb RFID cho \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a th\u1ebb UHF khi g\u1eafn v\u00e0o tai \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt<\/li>\n<li>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ecdc v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecdc<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ea5t hay h\u1ecfng th\u1ebb<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng chip trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t (v\u00ed d\u1ee5: b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, amoniac)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng v\u00f2ng l\u1eb7p kh\u00e9p k\u00edn v\u00e0 m\u1edf, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m, ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c nhau trong su\u1ed1t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang trong h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t th\u1ecbt.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/chiprfid.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41L3MrYF1mL.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3286\" src=\"https:\/\/chiprfid.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41L3MrYF1mL-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41L3MrYF1mL-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41L3MrYF1mL-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41L3MrYF1mL-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/41L3MrYF1mL.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng RFID cho \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1edbi \u00edt nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng quan r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt th\u00f4ng qua h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, ng\u00e0nh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 b\u00e1n l\u1ebb th\u1ecbt s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n n\u0103ng su\u1ea5t, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u th\u1eddi gian, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kho, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu h\u1ed3i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p l\u00f4 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m \u0111\u1ed9c, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/chiprfid.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/617Np0UyuSL._SX522_.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3287\" src=\"https:\/\/chiprfid.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/617Np0UyuSL._SX522_-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/617Np0UyuSL._SX522_-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/617Np0UyuSL._SX522_-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/617Np0UyuSL._SX522_-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/dientu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/617Np0UyuSL._SX522_.jpg 522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i gia s\u00fac kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u1edd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd